# Dev Build Icons

This directory contains icons for the development build of Mort.

## Required files:
- 32x32.png
- 128x128.png
- 128x128@2x.png
- icon.icns (macOS)
- icon.ico (Windows)
- icon.png

## Generation

To generate dev icons with a purple tint from production icons:

```bash
# Using ImageMagick
for f in ../icons/*.png; do
  convert "$f" -modulate 100,100,150 "$(basename $f)"
done

# Recreate .icns for macOS
iconutil -c icns icon.iconset -o icon.icns
```
